.NET Framework 3.5.name: VRTK_BaseGrabAttach
.NET Framework 3.5.summary: The Base Grab Attach script is an abstract class that all grab attach script inherit.
.NET Framework 3.5.remarks: As this is an abstract class, it cannot be applied directly to a game object and performs no logic.

methods.name: CreateTrackPoint(Transform controllerPoint, GameObject currentGrabbedObject, GameObject currentGrabbingObject, bool customTrackPoint)
methods.summary: The CreateTrackPoint method sets up the point of grab to track on the grabbed object.
methods.returns: The transform of the created track point.

params.value: The point on the controller where the grab was initiated.
The object that is currently being grabbed.
The object that is currently doing the grabbing.
A reference to whether the created track point is an auto generated custom object.
